    <item>
      <title>汇丰称中国政策支持将产生“提振效应”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/china-policy-support-to-have-lifting-effect-hsbc-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行刘静表示，中国央行周二宣布的政策支持是为了确保经济“能够实现 5% 的增长目标”。刘静还讨论了明年再次降息的可能性，并表示北京可能会推出进一步的财政刺激措施。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-24/china-policy-support-to-have-lifting-effect-hsbc-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 02:19:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师称中国措施凸显支撑股市的紧迫性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/strategists-divided-on-market-outlook-after-china-s-bold-moves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员和策略师表示，中国央行的一系列令人震惊的声明将在短期内给股市和债市带来提振，但他们对于其影响将持续多久存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/strategists-divided-on-market-outlook-after-china-s-bold-moves</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 02:15:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>远洋集团债权人对英国重组策略提出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/sino-ocean-creditors-raise-alarm-over-uk-restructuring-tactic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[远洋集团控股的一些债权人对这家中国建筑商在英国法庭寻求重组策略表示担忧，他们试图避免可能对他们不公平的裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/sino-ocean-creditors-raise-alarm-over-uk-restructuring-tactic</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 02:03:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将允许基金和券商利用中国人民银行资金购买股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-to-allow-funds-brokers-to-tap-pboc-funding-to-buy-stocks-m1frm2al</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国将允许基金和券商利用央行资金购买股票，这是旨在提振经济和提振投资者情绪的一系列措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-to-allow-funds-brokers-to-tap-pboc-funding-to-buy-stocks-m1frm2al</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:36:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北京采取一系列措施刺激经济，铁矿石价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iron-ore-spikes-as-beijing-takes-slew-of-steps-to-aid-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国宣布一系列促进增长的措施之后，铁矿石价格飙升，提振了全球最大进口国的需求前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iron-ore-spikes-as-beijing-takes-slew-of-steps-to-aid-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:34:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国十年期债券收益率首次跌至 2%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-s-10-year-bond-yield-falls-to-2-for-first-time-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国央行宣布一揽子货币政策宽松措施以支持经济增长，中国基准债券收益率有史以来首次跌至 2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-s-10-year-bond-yield-falls-to-2-for-first-time-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:18:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国宣布全面支持措施后油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-24</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国政府出台一系列经济政策支持措施，以及以色列对黎巴嫩真主党目标实施大规模袭击导致中东局势持续紧张，导致油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-24</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 23:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国经济刺激计划提振亚洲股市：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行宣布刺激措施，以实现今年的经济增长目标并阻止股市抛售，随后亚洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 22:46:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行观察家对自民党选举的关注集中在一位候选人身上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/boj-watchers-focus-on-ldp-election-comes-down-to-one-candidate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行观察人士正密切关注日本执政党自民党领导人选举，以了解其可能对货币政策产生的影响，并将注意力集中在一位坚决主张维持宽松立场的人士身上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/boj-watchers-focus-on-ldp-election-comes-down-to-one-candidate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 13:11:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
